channel.title: Changes Help!
channel.description: This is the story. I wanted to make a new teleport command and remove and add a few commands and I did and I noticed i have another client.java in the folder Data. So I update both client.java's and i compile and then i log in and test out the new stuff and it dose not work! It used to work so if i updated things and compiled but now it dose not :confused:! So can you please tell me how to fix the problem i know its vague but i hope its enough info if it isn't replay back and ask for more info.

item.title: Changes Help!
item.dc:creator: @Gh0stb4rr4g3 Gh0stb4rr4g3
item.description:
@Gh0stb4rr4g3 wrote:

Delete 1 client.java or just take it out of your server file.

You only need 1. And you can also only use one.

Btw quote from the rules:

6) Topic titles, use a brief descriptive title, a title such as "NEEEEED HELLLLLLLLLLLLLLLLLLLLLLLLLLPPPPPPPPPPPPPPPPPPPPPPPPPP FAST!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!" is just annoying and won't really help you get the help you need any faster.
